letting it slide this time.

17
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:32,540
But

18
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:34,420
don't let me see you

19
00:01:34,940 --> 00:01:36,180
in Kunyang again.

20
00:01:36,860 --> 00:01:37,660
Next time,

21
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:39,180
nobody

22
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:41,420
can save you.

23
00:01:42,460 --> 00:01:43,140
Let's go.

24
00:01:43,580 --> 00:01:44,660
Stay out of my way!

25
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:47,580
