27
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:52,660
But he was paid to do this.

28
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:53,940
Just doing his job.

29
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:56,340
Here's the idea.

30
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:59,340
Let me apologize on his behalf.

31
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:07,780
This is for your medical expenses
and compensation.

32
00:02:09,340 --> 00:02:10,340
Hao, please accept it.

33
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:16,460
You're a class act, man.

34
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:18,420
Respectable.

35
00:02:21,140 --> 00:02:22,900
What should I call you?

36
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:25,620
My last name is Jiang.

37
00:02:25,620 --> 00:02:28,260
Just call me Mr. Jiang.

38
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:30,420
Mr. Jiang.

39
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:31,780
See you.

40
00:02:32,620 --> 00:02:33,260
Let's go.

41
