will only make me more motivated.

584
00:33:19,580 --> 00:33:20,180
Alright then.

585
00:33:20,620 --> 00:33:21,580
Take your time getting settled.

586
00:33:21,820 --> 00:33:22,660
If you need anything,

587
00:33:22,660 --> 00:33:24,420
just reach out to your secretary, Li.

588
00:33:44,540 --> 00:33:45,140
Dad,

589
00:33:49,740 --> 00:33:52,100
what were you doing here
all these years?

590
00:33:53,020 --> 00:33:54,020
Where do I

591
00:33:55,540 --> 00:33:56,940
even start?

592
00:34:02,060 --> 00:34:02,740
You said

593
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:04,780
the simplest way

594
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:06,060
is often the most effective.

595
00:34:09,180 --> 00:34:10,100
Let's get started.

596
00:34:10,700 --> 00:34:11,460
Mr. Jiang.

597
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:12,420
It's me.

598
00:34:13,580 --> 00:34:15,460
I think Sanmahu's about to snap.

599
00:34:15,900 --> 00:34:17,020
He's on the edge,

600
00:34:17,220 --> 00:34:18,340
ready to go all out.

601
00:34:18,900 --> 00:34:19,900
Then let him.

602
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:22,620
But you said the timing wasn't right.

603
00:34:23,060 --> 00:34:23,820
Should we wait a bit longer?

604
00:34:24,260 --> 00:34:25,620
Plans change.

605
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:27,300
But maybe it's for the best.

606
00:34:28,220 --> 00:34:29,460
Stick with him for now.

607
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:32,060
I'll call him tonight

608
00:34:32,260 --> 00:34:33,740
and tell him what to do.

609
00:34:34,420 --> 00:34:35,820
Understood.

610
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:44,380
Do you need something?

611
00:34:45,700 --> 00:34:46,540
I looked through the materials,

612
00:34:46,580 --> 00:34:47,340
but I couldn't understand them.

613
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:48,700
Can I see the company's

614
00:34:48,740 --> 00:34:49,980
recent financial statements?

615
00:34:50,020 --> 00:34:51,140
So I can get a clearer picture

616
00:34:51,180 --> 00:34:52,180
of the financial situation.

617
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:53,900
I'll have the accountant
bring them to you.

618
00:34:53,940 --> 00:34:54,900
I already asked.

619
00:34:54,940 --> 00:34:55,980
They're closing the books
at the end of the month,

620
00:34:56,020 --> 00:34:56,940
so we'll have to wait until next month.

621
00:34:57,580 --> 00:34:58,420
Do you have a backup copy?

622
00:35:01,100 --> 00:35:01,580
Yes.

623
00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:02,620
Just a moment.

624
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:21,620
Everything is here.

625
00:35:21,860 --> 00:35:22,740
Let me know

626
00:35:22,780 --> 00:35:23,620
if you have any questions.

627
00:35:24,340 --> 00:35:25,100
Thank you.

628
00:35:38,020 --> 00:35:38,780
From Majia Village?

629
00:35:39,900 --> 00:35:40,660
Yeah.

630
00:35:41,300 --> 00:35:42,700
Who's Sanmahu to you?

631
00:35:43,420 --> 00:35:44,180
He's my uncle.

632
00:35:44,660 --> 00:35:45,900
Also my idol.

633
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:47,980
Have you seen him lately?

634
00:35:49,380 --> 00:35:50,140
No.

635
00:35:51,900 --> 00:35:52,900
Think carefully.

636
00:35:53,420 --> 00:35:54,180
Have you?

637
00:35:54,380 --> 00:35:56,180
You can say I have if you want.

638
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:58,540
But I don't know where he is.

639
00:35:58,700 --> 00:35:59,340
Officer,

640
00:35:59,620 --> 00:36:01,220
is that okay?

641
00:36:05,220 --> 00:36:05,980
Kid,

642
00:36:07,580 --> 00:36:08,660
do you know who I am?

643
00:36:10,020 --> 00:36:10,820
Mr. Tu.

644
00:36:11,620 --> 00:36:12,620
Heard of me?

645
00:36:15,860 --> 00:36:18,900
I know you guys from Majia Village
have guts and can't be messed with.

646
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:20,180
But let me tell you,

647
00:36:20,580 --> 00:36:22,500
ten years ago,
I could've crushed you guys.

648
00:36:22,540 --> 00:36:24,100
And I still can.

649
00:36:25,020 --> 00:36:25,940
Think hard.

650
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:27,620
Say it when you've figured it out.

651
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:40,260
Mr. Tu.

652
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:44,380
Mr. Tu!

653
00:36:45,580 --> 00:36:46,140
Mr. Tu.

654
00:36:49,020 --> 00:36:50,260
I'd like to

655
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:52,540
treat you and the other guys
in First Division tonight.

656
00:36:52,780 --> 00:36:53,540
How about it?

657
00:36:55,900 --> 00:36:57,020
No other intentions.

658
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,980
The bureau has decided to
merge the cases for investigation.

659
00:36:59,020 --> 00:37:01,060
