660
00:37:01,340 --> 00:37:03,180
You've been going against him
for over 20 years.

661
00:37:03,340 --> 00:37:04,500
You're the veteran here.

662
00:37:04,660 --> 00:37:05,820
I can handle drug dealers,

663
00:37:05,900 --> 00:37:07,780
