with an cunning fox like Sanmahu,

664
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:09,180
I'll need to learn from you.

665
00:37:09,900 --> 00:37:10,420
Alright.

666
00:37:11,060 --> 00:37:11,940
At seven tonight.

667
00:37:12,300 --> 00:37:13,100
I'll pick the place.

668
00:37:13,820 --> 00:37:14,660
You're paying.

669
00:37:16,100 --> 00:37:16,860
Alright.

670
00:37:22,540 --> 00:37:23,100
Mr. Sanmahu.

671
00:37:24,180 --> 00:37:24,940
Have something to eat.

672
00:37:35,900 --> 00:37:37,380
No sense of timing at all.

673
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:39,820
I'm starting to think

674
00:37:40,380 --> 00:37:41,620
this Jiang guy

675
00:37:41,660 --> 00:37:42,620
is a fraud!

676
00:37:47,980 --> 00:37:48,540
Hello?

677
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:50,180
Mr. Jiang.

678
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:52,020
Finally, your called.

679
00:37:52,580 --> 00:37:55,140
I heard what happened during the day.

680
00:37:56,020 --> 00:37:57,260
Then do it.

681
00:37:57,740 --> 00:37:58,660
Mr. Sanmahu,

682
00:37:59,100 --> 00:38:01,020
let me remind you,

683
00:38:01,060 --> 00:38:04,220
taking action against Tu Hongjiang
is a big deal.

684
00:38:04,900 --> 00:38:06,980
He's a fixer for the law-abiding,

685
00:38:07,020 --> 00:38:08,500
a grim reaper for the underworld.

686
00:38:09,180 --> 00:38:10,300
If you're going to move,

687
00:38:10,620 --> 00:38:12,300
make it clean.

688
00:38:13,780 --> 00:38:17,060
No hesitation, no loose ends.

689
00:38:17,220 --> 00:38:18,020
Either

690
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:19,740
take him out in one strike,

691
00:38:20,540 --> 00:38:21,300
or

692
00:38:21,540 --> 00:38:22,900
be prepared to burn together.

693
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:24,300
Understood.

694
00:38:26,140 --> 00:38:27,260
Perfect, Mr. Jiang.

695
00:38:28,620 --> 00:38:29,780
With your support,

696
00:38:29,900 --> 00:38:31,980
I'm more confident

697
00:38:32,380 --> 00:38:33,540
about all the scores

698
00:38:33,780 --> 00:38:35,020
with him.

699
00:38:35,180 --> 00:38:36,100
Actually,

700
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:39,380
I have a more thorough, reliable plan.

701
00:38:39,700 --> 00:38:42,780
Today's incident was fate.

702
00:38:43,180 --> 00:38:45,020
Then let's just follow it

703
00:38:45,260 --> 00:38:46,620
and finish him tomorrow.

704
00:38:47,140 --> 00:38:49,860
Let me remind you again.

705
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:52,860
Don't act rashly.

706
00:38:52,980 --> 00:38:55,500
Stick to my plan.

707
00:38:56,060 --> 00:38:58,300
If all goes well,

708
00:38:58,460 --> 00:39:00,280
I'll meet you at the destination,

709
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:01,000
[October 4th, T766,
Xiatong to Shannan, Tu Hongjiang]

710
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:03,860
the very place where you

711
00:39:04,380 --> 00:39:05,300
take down Tu Hongjiang.

712
00:39:05,500 --> 00:39:06,260
Mr. Jiang,

713
00:39:07,100 --> 00:39:08,500
thank you for your full support.

714
00:39:08,780 --> 00:39:09,460
I will

715
00:39:09,980 --> 00:39:11,300
never forget it.

716
00:39:11,860 --> 00:39:13,100
Look forward to meeting you.

717
00:39:35,780 --> 00:39:38,220
[Back for More]

718
00:39:38,220 --> 00:39:38,980
Kid.

719
00:39:39,180 --> 00:39:39,980
No, no.

720
00:39:41,020 --> 00:39:41,860
Mr. Zhan.

721
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:43,260
Hey, don't.

722
00:39:44,860 --> 00:39:46,020
By age,

723
00:39:46,300 --> 00:39:47,700
I am almost as old as your uncle.

724
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:49,460
By seniority,

725
00:39:49,940 --> 00:39:51,100
