726
00:39:51,540 --> 00:39:53,100
Your father was my master.

727
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:55,380
He taught me a lot.

728
00:39:59,020 --> 00:39:59,780
How to conduct myself

729
00:40:00,260 --> 00:40:01,060
and how to handle things.

730
00:40:02,740 --> 00:40:04,340
I'll never forget that.

731
00:40:07,940 --> 00:40:09,500
I know sometimes

732
00:40:10,340 --> 00:40:12,060
