739
00:40:29,580 --> 00:40:31,340
My master is my master.

740
00:40:33,220 --> 00:40:34,100
That won't change.

741
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:37,340
I'll remember that.

742
00:43:05,620 --> 00:43:07,700
How was this money collected?

743
00:43:11,420 --> 00:43:13,660
Why is Sanmahu on here too?

744
00:43:14,660 --> 00:43:15,620
Dad?

745
00:43:20,540 --> 00:43:23,060
This ledger is definitely fishy.

746
00:43:31,940 --> 00:43:32,980
[Back for More]

747
00:43:32,980 --> 00:43:33,740
Alright.

748
00:43:34,220 --> 00:43:35,180
Everyone, head back now.

749
00:43:35,180 --> 00:43:36,340
We've got work tomorrow.

750
00:43:36,420 --> 00:43:37,300
Go on, get going.

751
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:38,220
Let me walk you home.

752
00:43:38,780 --> 00:43:39,500
Don't bother.

753
00:43:39,500 --> 00:43:40,660
In Xiatong,

754
00:43:40,740 --> 00:43:42,820
I could find my way even blindfolded.

755
00:43:42,980 --> 00:43:44,140
Go back.

756
00:43:44,420 --> 00:43:45,220
I'll get going then.

757
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:45,980
You all go ahead.

758
00:43:45,980 --> 00:43:46,940
I'll walk him home.

759
00:43:47,460 --> 00:43:47,900
Bye.

760
00:43:47,900 --> 00:43:48,420
Mr. Tu, I've got things to do.

761
00:43:48,420 --> 00:43:48,900
I'll head out.

762
00:43:48,900 --> 00:43:49,540
Alright.

763
00:43:49,620 --> 00:43:50,420
Mr. Tu, take care.

764
00:43:50,420 --> 00:43:51,380
Sneaking off early again?

765
00:43:56,980 --> 00:43:57,780
What's your problem?

766
00:43:58,420 --> 00:43:59,420
Watch where you're going.

767
00:44:00,180 --> 00:44:01,180
The road's wide,

768
00:44:01,340 --> 00:44:02,300
