769
00:44:03,260 --> 00:44:04,700
Mr. Sanmahu has a message for you.

770
00:44:05,180 --> 00:44:07,180
Tomorrow, T766, hard seat.

771
00:44:08,100 --> 00:44:09,260
If you've got any guts,

772
00:44:09,540 --> 00:44:10,900
come alone.

773
00:44:11,820 --> 00:44:12,700
Tell him

774
00:44:12,860 --> 00:44:13,740
I'll be there on time.

775
00:44:22,380 --> 00:44:23,780
Tomorrow's a big day.

776
00:44:24,340 --> 00:44:25,780
Should I do something?

777
00:44:25,860 --> 00:44:27,380
Be ready.

778
00:44:28,740 --> 00:44:30,260
Don't worry about Tu Hongjiang.

779
00:44:31,580 --> 00:44:33,060
Just keep your eyes on Sanmahu.

780
00:44:34,580 --> 00:44:37,060
Whether he kills Tu Hongjiang or not

781
00:44:37,060 --> 00:44:38,060
