782
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:41,300
What matters is whether
you get the chance to take over

783
00:44:41,980 --> 00:44:42,980
Xiatong's business.

784
00:44:45,380 --> 00:44:46,180
Understood.

785
00:44:46,860 --> 00:44:47,900
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

786
00:44:48,820 --> 00:44:49,740
You're right.

787
00:44:50,860 --> 00:44:52,060
May the best man win.

788
00:44:52,340 --> 00:44:53,180
It's him or me.

789
00:44:53,420 --> 00:44:55,140
Tomorrow, only one of us two

790
00:44:56,820 --> 00:44:58,180
will be coming to see you.

791
00:45:12,240 --> 00:45:17,080
